{
  "id": "693999cedbe40e2805bc60a5",
  "title": "荻風が2025年に読んだ本",
  "created": 1765382682,
  "updated": 1777725776,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "693999cedbe40e2805bc60a5",
      "text": "荻風が2025年に読んだ本",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765382682,
      "updated": 1765382682
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b42d00000000001e2af4",
      "text": "[井戸端アドベントカレンダー2025]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765389358,
      "updated": 1765389362
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b43300000000001e2af5",
      "text": "　記事っぽくはないかもしれない[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765389363,
      "updated": 1765389371
    },
    {
      "id": "69399a1a0000000000cb4490",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765382682,
      "updated": 1765382847
    },
    {
      "id": "69399a290000000000cb44a3",
      "text": "🥈さおだけ屋はなぜ潰れないのか？",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765382698,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad1",
      "text": "　[会計学]の初歩の初歩を教えてくれる",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765525449
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad2",
      "text": " 　とっつきにくい会計学を身近な疑問から解説してくれた",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765525446
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad3",
      "text": "　魅力的な問で解説してくれるので非常に読みやすかった[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad4",
      "text": "🥉Z世代",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad5",
      "text": "　[Z世代]の特徴を詳しく解説してくれる本",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765525455
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad6",
      "text": "　　こういう話が好きなので非常に面白いネタ",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad7",
      "text": "　流行は既に移り変わりすぎたので例に挙げられた流行がわからないこと多々あった",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad8",
      "text": "＃100日チャレンジ",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ad9",
      "text": "継続する技術",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ada",
      "text": "[『「好き」を言語化する技術』]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765389395
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2adb",
      "text": "52ヘルツのクジラたち",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2adc",
      "text": "　自分と環境が違いすぎてあまりのめり込めなかったが、かなり感情が揺さぶられたのでいい小説なのだろうと思う[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2add",
      "text": "22世紀の民主主義",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ade",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2adf",
      "text": "有名だから読んだ本",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae0",
      "text": " 嫌われる勇気",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae1",
      "text": " アイデアの作り方",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae2",
      "text": " バレットジャーナル",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae3",
      "text": " リーダブルコード",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae4",
      "text": " チーズはどこに消えた?",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae5",
      "text": " この分野は全体的にそこそこの満足度だったかなあ[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae7",
      "text": "著者のファンなので読んだ本",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae8",
      "text": " 🥇[会話の0.2秒を言語学する]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765389405
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2ae9",
      "text": " 　会話の話者交代の間に行われている、さまざまな言語の営みについて言語学から解析しようとする本",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aea",
      "text": " 　水野さんが今読みたい本を書いたという触れ込み通り、ゆる言語学ラジオをかなり聞いている[wogikaze.icon]にとっても新しい情報が多く読んでて楽しかった",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aeb",
      "text": " きょう、ゴリラをうえたよ",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aec",
      "text": " 言語の本質",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aed",
      "text": " POWER麻雀の極意",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2aef",
      "text": "まだ読んでる途中",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2af0",
      "text": "　作って学ぶOSのしくみ",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2af1",
      "text": "　[plurality]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765389382
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2af2",
      "text": "　暗号解読",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1765388597
    },
    {
      "id": "6939b13600000000001e2af3",
      "text": "　[はじめてのGTD]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1765388597,
      "updated": 1777725776
    },
    {
      "id": "693a049e0000000000592ae5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
